				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2283210/scp-3111#post-2833690</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 26 May 2017 20:41:16 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Spookerman</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3068706</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Pretty good. An SCP in which an object that facilitates a sort of time travel that also links to a mysterious organization or known group of interest that has the ability to invent SCPs, even on the personal purposes of their members. All along, these things are shown and implied through the story of it being given away as a Christmas present instead of being dumped as exposition.</p> <p>+1 in my book.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
